citations:
    citation-affc-brienne-crossroads:
        source: source-affc
        properties:
            locator: "Brienne VIII"
            text_from_source: "They came upon the first corpse a mile from the crossroads."
            accessed: "2026-03-06"
        notes: "Brienne, Podrick, and Ser Hyle arrive at the crossroads inn (the old Masha Heddle inn). Along the road they pass dozens of hanged men with salt packed in their mouths — victims of the Brotherhood Without Banners. At the inn they find Gendry working as a blacksmith and the innkeeper Willow Heddle. They also encounter a Hound-helmed outlaw and members of the Brotherhood. Biter attacks Brienne and bites off part of her face before Gendry kills him with a spear. Brienne and companions are captured by the Brotherhood Without Banners."
